        "Title": "Vadim Yusov",
        "Type": "Interview",
        "Description": "Director Andrei Tarkovsky relied on cinematographer Vadim Yusov for the stunning images of The Steamroller and the Violin, Ivan\u0027s Childhood, Andrei Rublev, and finally, Solaris. In this interview, Yusov reflects on their relationship, Tarkovsky\u0027s perfectionism, and their meeting in Italy before Tarkovsky\u0027s death in 1986.",
        "Chapters": []
